io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.general.service.impl.config

Class RestaurantTestConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.general.service.impl.config.RestaurantTestConfig

  • @Configuration
 @Profile(value="junit")
public class RestaurantTestConfig
extends Object
    This configuration class provides @Bean annotated methods. It is applied to a test class by using the following class annotation: @SpringApplicationConfiguration(classes = RestaurantTestConfig.class). Hence, beans provided by @Bean annotated methods will not be available outside the test configuration.

    See AbstractRestServiceTest as an example.
